OL,7,FA street sweeper is packing his bags
OL,8,Fto Portugal after getting a birthday
OL,9,Fsurprise he thought might never happen.
OL,11,FPaul Spiers has been keeping the
OL,12,Fstreets of Beckenham in south east
OL,13,FLondon clean since 2017.
OL,15,FHe's so popular locals set up an
OL,16,Fonline fundraiser to raise money to
OL,17,Fsend him on a trip abroad for his
OL,18,Fbirthday.
