OL,7,FThe GoFundMe page which raised more
OL,8,Fthan #3,000 was set up by local
OL,9,Fresident Lisa Knight.
OL,11,F"Me and Paul have a special connection
OL,12,Fbecause he always listens to Elvis and
OL,13,FI'm named Lisa-Marie and it's just
OL,14,Ffollowed on from there," Lisa said.
OL,16,F"I thought it was sad the people of
OL,17,FBeckenham never got to use their money
OL,18,Ftowards what they wanted it for," she
OL,19,Fadded.
