OL,7,FWhen Paul thought his holiday dream
OL,8,Fwas over he suddenly won a holiday
OL,9,Fcompetition to Portugal with On The
OL,10,FBeach worth #3,000.
OL,12,FHis empoyer Veolia said: "We are
OL,13,Fdelighted that Paul can travel to
OL,14,FPortugal for a well-deserved holiday
OL,15,Fthanks to his competition win. To make
OL,16,Fsure he can go and enjoy his holiday
OL,17,Fwhenever he chooses we are giving him
OL,18,Fan extra week of paid leave to enjoy."
